After crossing the bridge I shudder.[p]
The temperature is gradually declining. [p]
Or maybe it is just a result of the thing inside me that produces nervousness and fear.[p]
On this wide road there is not a single motorcycle running.[p]
I am running right down the center of it.[p]
If I continue forward, Alchemilla Hospital should be on the right.[p]


