An old building appears in the thick fog.[p]
On the signboard "Alchemilla" appears in faded letters. [p]
Its eeriness caused me to hesitate for an instant, but in the next moment I placed my hand on the cold gate.[p]
I open the heavy hospital gate, and then open the door directly to my right that has "Entrance" written on it.[p]


